xt":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19591,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/07\/26\/al-ala-ghashiyah-jumuah-eid\/","url_meta":{"origin":5047,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Eid: Surat al-A&#8217;la and al-Ghashiyah in Eid, Friday prayers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 26, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Num\u2019an ibn Bashir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would recite in the two Eid prayers and in the Friday prayer the chapters, \u201cGlorify the name of your Lord the Most High,\u201d (87:1) and, \u201cHas there come to you the news of the overwhelming?\u201d (88:1).\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5029,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/12\/sing-play-eid\/","url_meta":{"origin":5047,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Eid: Singing and playing on Eid","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 12, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, came to my house when two girls were beside me singing songs of Bu\u2019ath. The Prophet laid down and turned his face to the other side. Then, Abu Bakr came in and spoke to me harshly, saying, \u201cMusical\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5037,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/12\/prophet-dates-eid-al-fitr\/","